  • Enum Constant Details

    • EMP

      public static final UseAction EMP
      Use EMP action. Only feasible if the player has an EMP power up, will not hit hard obstacles on using it, is behind the opponent, and has the opponent within the EMP range.

    • CYBERTRUCK

      public static final UseAction CYBERTRUCK
      Use TWEET action. Only feasible if the player has a TWEET power up and will not hit hard obstacles on using it.

    • BOOST

      public static final UseAction BOOST
      Use BOOST action. Only feasible if the player has a BOOST power up, will not hit hard obstacles on using it, and is not currently boosting.

    • OIL

      public static final UseAction OIL
      Use OIL action. Only feasible if the player has an OIL power up, will not hit hard obstacles on using it, and is ahead of opponent.

    • LIZARD

      public static final UseAction LIZARD
      Use LIZARD action. Only feasible if the player has a LIZARD power up, will not hit hard obstacles on using it, has obstacles ahead, and will not land on an obstacle after using lizard power up.

    • EMP_FORCE

      public static final UseAction EMP_FORCE
      Force-use EMP action. Similar to use EMP action but ignore hard obstacles.

    • CYBERTRUCK_FORCE

      public static final UseAction CYBERTRUCK_FORCE
      Force-use TWEET action. Similar to use TWEET action but ignore hard obstacles.

    • BOOST_FORCE

      public static final UseAction BOOST_FORCE

    • OIL_FORCE

      public static final UseAction OIL_FORCE
      Force-use OIL action. Similar to use OIL action but ignore hard obstacles.

    • LIZARD_FORCE

      public static final UseAction LIZARD_FORCE
      Force-use LIZARD action. Similar to use LIZARD action but ignore hard obstacles and landing block.
